  "detailed_description": "Platformer and action game features come together in Hop Man, an entertaining multiplayer game. To solve the secret of this perplexing universe, you must navigate through all of the traps and overcome a variety of platforms and items. Play by yourself or with friends—playing together is usually more enjoyable. Along the way, there will be amusing references and Easter eggs.",
